<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>System Configuration on Tech Notebook</title><link>https://wiki.deimos.fr/categories/system-configuration/</link><description>Recent content in System Configuration on Tech Notebook</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 17:45:45 +0200</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://wiki.deimos.fr/categories/system-configuration/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Activating the Numeric Keypad</title><link>https://wiki.deimos.fr/activer-le-pave-numerique/</link><pubDate>Tue, 22 Jan 2008 08:49:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://wiki.deimos.fr/activer-le-pave-numerique/</guid><description>&lt;p>To have the numlock activated in console and under X:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>In console mode:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="9427678" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>echo &amp;#34;LEDS=&amp;#43;num&amp;#34; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /etc/console-tools/config&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>In X Window System:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="2b03e63" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>apt-get install numlockx&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>